Java 12 features list (all major ones):

Switch Expressions (preview)

New String method: indent(int n)

New String method: transform(Function)

Compact Number Formatting (NumberFormat.getCompactNumberInstance())

Teeing Collector (Collectors.teeing())

Files mismatch method (Files.mismatch(Path, Path))

Shenandoah Garbage Collector (experimental)

Microbenchmark Suite (jmh integration in JDK build)

JVM Constants API

Default CDS Archives (Class Data Sharing by default)

Abortable Mixed Collections for G1 GC

Switch Expression JEP updates (preview improvements)